odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-F (YRG 9-F), Yale College student records.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The records were transferred from the Office of the Registrar for the Faculty of Arts and Sciences, 2002-2012.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Office of the Registrar, Faculty of Arts and Sciences, Yale University, Student Records (RU 922). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of transcripts and grade sheets for students in Yale College and Sheffield Scientific School maintained by the Yale Faculty of Arts and Sciences Office of the Registrar.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Accession 2013-A-073 consists of transcripts and other students records removed by the Office of the Registrar from previously archived files for digitization. The records were returned to the archive as a group without reference to their original location and were accessioned as a group by the repository.
